name: Tierren: Industrial Conglomerate
abilities: You can use construction generated by Tierren: Industrial Conglomerate on any asset.

name: Tierren: Megabuilders
abilities: Add 2 construction tokens to Tierren: Megabuilders. You may spend them as generated construction during the resource utilization phase.

name: Tierren: Resilient Infrastructure
abilities: Newly constructed megastructures start with +1 infrastructure

name: ENIAK: Unbottled Reactors
abilities: When any of your spacecraft moves do 1 damage to all enemy spacecraft in the starting orbital

name: ENIAK: Predictive Oracle
abilities: Your espionage operations gain the trigger "When you generate at least 3 influence."

name: ENIAK: Robotic Settlements
abilities: Assets and megastructures you control don't take damage on a roll of 2 or less.

name: Magonia
abilities: When Magonia takes damage, it does 1 damage to every spacecraft in orbit.

name: Juniffer
abilities: Treaties on Juniffer do not need upkeep. Juniffer can host 1 more treaty.

name: Paloma
abilities: Neither Paloma or spacecraft in its orbit can be the triggers or targets of espionage cards.

name: Lagrange Construction Yard
abilities: Ships constructed at Lagrange Construction Yard cost one less construction.

name: Terrarium Project
abilities: Spacecraft moving from Terrarium Project do not pay delta-vee for intervening assets.

name: Olivarium
abilities: Enemy spacecraft in orbit around Olivarium must pay 2 delta-vee or take 2 damage at the end of the round.

name: Foundation
abilities: When Foundation is activated for research, draw 2 cards and put one on the bottom of your deck.
